text: Aleksandr Mordovin (, 3 February 1873 - 31 March 1938) was a Russian fencer. He competed in three events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1873 births Category:1938 deaths Category:Russian male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Russia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
